the משנה *Mishnah*, we'll end here and we'll pick up tomorrow with

950
00:42:42,600 --> 00:42:46,240
the discussion about Rabbi Akiva and the חכמים *Chachamim* about which blood

951
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:49,200
gets invalidated when you bring it into the היכל *Heichal*, is it

